Create directories in Linux 
---------------------------

>mkdir dir1 dir2 dir3
>ls -l
>mkdir d{1..4}



How to install and remove tree package
sudo apt install tree
sudo apt-get --purge remove tree

-tree command can be used to view dir structure clearly

>mkdir --help 
>mkdir -v <directories> 
creating child directories  (p parent)
#mkdir -p L1/L2/L3
 or
 mkdir -p -v L1/L2/L3


to view recursively
>ls -R L1


 giving permission to directories
 mkdir -m a=rwx [directories] 
            -to all user rwx